				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="Mars Memorandum: A Solitaire Strategic Game About Mars Colonization" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>&amp;quot;Mars is there, waiting to be reached.&amp;quot;&amp;#10;Buzz Aldrin&amp;#10;Live the dangers and challenges of colonizing Mars in our Mars Memorandum strategy game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mars Memorandum is a solitaire strategic game, where it simulates the creation of a colony in Martian soil. The main objective of the player is to develop and maintain a population of 2000 settlers despite the problems and possible natural events.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Components:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     1 Rules booklet&amp;#10;     1 board with Mars map&amp;#10;     1 Recon Manual&amp;#10;     Resource and Facilities Markers&amp;#10;     General Control Board of the Colony&amp;#10;     1 player aid&amp;#10;     3d models for print&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You need also 1 six-sided dice (d6). You can borrow from another game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mars Memorandum is a game of resource management, reasoning and luck. &amp;#10;The goal is to build and maintain a Martian colony for 2000 inhabitants in 30 game turns. The player should rely heavily on his reasoning to develop the full potency of the colony in all its aspects.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
